                            <comment id="12483814" author="asankha" created="Sat, 24 Mar 2007 06:38:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reply to client will have a RelatesTo to the original message from the client&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The message exchange between Synapse and any backend service will have seperate relationships if addressing is engaged&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12595487" author="evanthika" created="Fri, 9 May 2008 07:23:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Now the &amp;lt;Relates-To&amp;gt;tag is displayed without duplicating. Fixed in 1.2_QA_B1. The issue will be closed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
